data.description: Nice ranch-style home nestled in the heart of Harvest, AL.  This great opportunity is situated on a generous 0.64-acre corner lot, offering both space and privacy. The home is characterized by low maintenance, full brick construction that promises durability and timeless appeal. The interior boasts spacious bedrooms and well-appointed bathrooms. The main suite is a comfortable retreat, featuring a bay window that bathes the room in natural light. This beautiful, ranch-style home at 218 Waypoint Circle in Harvest, AL is the epitome of comfortable, spacious, and practical living. It's more than a house, it's a place you can truly call home. May be eligible for 100% Financing.
